.com%2Fgrowing-up-poor-homeless-help-make-better-parent-2024-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emy%20childhood%3C%2Fa%3E%20around%20friends%20and%20in%20the%20therapy%20room.%20Perhaps%20part%20of%20me%20hoped%20that%20journaling%20and%20the%20mindfulness%20work%20I%20was%20doing%20would%20be%20enough.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20my%20friend's%20question%20kept%20playing%20over%20in%20my%20brain.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat's%20when%20my%20psychologist%20guided%20me%20through%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fsurprising-forms-of-therapy-2019-2%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EInternal%20Family%20Systems%20(IFS)%3C%2Fa%3E%20therapy%2C%20a%20practice%20where%20I%20embodied%20myself%20at%20different%20ages.%20I%20remember%20%E2%80%94%20during%20a%20session%20%E2%80%94%20embodying%209-year-old%20Teresa.%20My%20dad%20was%20screaming%20at%20me%20because%20my%20running%20shoes%20were%20not%20organized%20in%20a%20straight%20line%20at%20the%20door.%20As%20I%20described%20the%20scene%20to%20my%20therapist%2C%20he%20responded%2C%20%26quot%3BNone%20of%20this%20was%20your%20fault.%26quot%3BTears%20fell%20down%20my%20cheek.%20It%20felt%20like%20my%20therapist%20was%20talking%20directly%20to%209-year-old%20Teresa%20%E2%80%94%20not%20to%2045-year-old%20Teresa.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20though%20both%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fguides%2Fparenting%2Fgenerational-trauma%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Echildhood%20trauma%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20burnout%20symptoms%20often%20overlap%2C%20the%20solution%20differs.%20Most%20traditional%20burnout%20recovery%20approaches%20overfocus%20on%20external%20solutions%20%E2%80%94%20like%20physical%20exercise%20or%20an%20adequate%20rest%20and%20sleep%20schedule.%20While%20these%20are%20healthy%20and%20self-care-promoting%2C%20for%20someone%20who%20has%20experienced%20childhood%20trauma%2C%20true%20relief%20comes%20from%20addressing%20your%20deeper%20needs%2C%20I%20learned.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cst