edia.%20BI%20has%20verified%20his%20employment%20and%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20West%20Coast-based%20engineer%2C%20who%20joined%20the%20company%20several%20years%20ago%2C%20gets%20nearly%20half%20of%20his%20base%20salary%20amount%20worth%20of%20restricted%20stock%20units%20(RSUs)%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20looking%20from%20a%20far%20distance%20and%20you%20say%20Nvidians%20are%20millionaires%2C%20yes%20absolutely%2C%20but%20that%20million%20doesn't%20go%20too%20far%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20because%20the%20stock%20has%20gone%20sky-high%2C%20there's%20an%20expectation%20that%20everybody%20has%20made%20a%20lot%20of%20money%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%20%26quot%3BIn%20reality%2C%20the%20RSUs%20you%20get%20is%20where%20the%20bulk%20of%20your%20exponential%20growth%20in%20wealth%20will%20be%20and%20not%20everybody%20will%20get%20a%20lot.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEven%20if%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-employees-rich-happy-problem-insiders-say-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Esome%20employees%3C%2Fa%3E%20get%20a%20lot%20of%20RSUs%20given%20to%20them%2C%20he%20said%20that%20they%20might%20not%20all%20have%20held%20onto%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BYou%20will%20end%20up%20cashing%20your%20stocks%20to%20meet%20your%20annual%20obligations%20in%20terms%20of%20personal%20taxes%2C%20property%20taxes%2C%20and%20any%20other%20expenses%20you%20will%20have%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%2C%20which%20has%20about%2026%2C000%20employees%2C%20has%20greatly%20benefited%20from%20the%20generative%20AI%20boom%20as%20its%20GPUs%20are%20key%20components%20for%20applications%20like%20ChatGPT.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIts%20stock%20has%20soared%20in%20the%20past%2012%20months%2C%20making%20it%20the%20most%20valuable%20company%20after%20Microsoft%20and%20Apple.%20However%2C%20Nvidia%20shares%20fell%2010%25%20on%20Friday%20and%20are%20now%20almost%20%24200%20below%20their%20March%20peak%2C%20leaving%20the%20company%20worth%20%241.9%20trillion.%20%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3EMisconception%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3ENvidia%20engineers%20are%20called%20%26quot%3Bindividual%20contributors%26quot%3B%20(IC)%20and%20are%20ranked%20from%20tier%201%20to%20tier%208.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20engineer%20BI%20spoke%20to%20is%20an%20IC%20level%20four.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20said%20that%20he's%20often%20asked%20in%20social%20settings%20how%20much%20he's%20making.%20However%2C%20the%20worker%20argues%20it's%20a%20misconception%20that%20all%20Nvidia%20staff%20are%20cash-rich%2C%20as%20much%20of%20their%20wealth%20is%20tied%20up%20in%20stock%2C%20with%20taxes%20also%20taking%20a%20big%20chunk%20out%20of%20their%20earnings.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20would%20be%20incorrect%20to%20consider%20a%20job%20at%20Nvidia%20as%20a%20way%20to%20turn%20a%20quick%20million%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHis%20base%20salary%20places%20him%20in%20one%20of%20the%20second-highest%20federal%20income%20tax%20brackets%2C%20with%20a%20rate%20of%2035%25.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOn%20top%20of%20that%2C%20he%20pays%20property%20taxes%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fwhat-is-social-security%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3ESocial%20Security%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20and%20Medicare%20levies.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E'Life%20happens'%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20argued%20that%20a%20million%20was%20%26quot%3Bnot%20a%20big%20number%26quot%3B%20in%20California%2C%20where%20Nvidia%20has%20four%20offices%2C%20as%20house%20prices%20and%20the%20cost%20of%20living%20are%20typically%20high.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20%26quot%3Blife%20happens%2C%26quot%3B%20meaning%20there%20are%20always%20unexpected%20bills%20or%20costs.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20biggest%20purchase%20he%20has%20made%20since%20cashing%20out%20some%20of%20his%20Nvidia%20stock%20was%20a%20%24250%2C000%20down%20payment%20on%20his%20three-bedroom%20house%2C%20which%20cost%20almost%20%241.4%20million%20in%202018.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere's%20also%20a%20cap%20on%20how%20many%20stock%20units%20workers%20can%20get.%20Even%20the%20most%20exemplary%20employees%20are%20capped%20at%20receiving%2050%25%20of%20their%20base%20salary%20in%20stock%20a%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20means%20that%20a%20Nvidia%20employee%20earning%20%241%20million%20a%20year%20may%20not%20be%20considered%20rich%20in%20a%20place%20like%20San%20Francisco.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Fhow-much-to-be-wealthy-new-york-san-francisco-dc-2023-6%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E2023%20Charles%20Schwab%20Modern%20Wealth%20Survey%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20you%20need%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%244.7%20million%20to%20be%20%26quot%3Bwealthy.%26quot%3B%3Cbr%3E%3Cbr%3EThere's%20also%20big%20pay%20disparities%20between%20Nvidians%20in%20the%20US%20and%20other%20countries.%20A%20software%20engineer%20in%20India%2C%20who%20is%20an%20IC%20level%203%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fnvidia-software-engineer-how-landed-job-preparation-culture-interviews-2024-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eearns%20a%20base%20salary%20of%20about%20%2419%2C000%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI'm%20still%20happy%20with%20where%20I%20am%20and%20I'm%20glad%20I've%20made%20it%2C%20but%20it's%20not%20as%20rosy%20as%20it%20looks%20from%20the%20outside%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20engineer%20said.%20%26quot%3BI'm%20really%20happy%20with%20the%20price%20Nvidia%20stock%20is%20trading%20at.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Nvidia%20Jensen%20Huang%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F655645fa36d588dc55d1975d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222692%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ENvidia%20CEO%20Jensen%20Huang.%3Cp%3EI-HWA%20CHENG%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20stock%20surge%20helped%20make%20CEO%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https