ck%20of%20my%20mind.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEverything%20changed%20when%20I%20found%20a%20Henry%20VIII%20outfit%20on%20Facebook%20Marketplace%20for%20%C2%A320%20(%2425)%20in%202021.%20I'd%20always%20wanted%20to%20own%20one%2C%20whether%20I'd%20wear%20it%20or%20not.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20decided%20to%20post%20a%20photo%20of%20myself%20wearing%20it%20on%20Facebook.%20Immediately%20messages%20flooded%20in%20telling%20me%20I%20bore%20a%20resemblance%20to%20the%20young%20King.%20A%20historical%20costumier%20saw%20the%20post%20and%20directed%20me%20to%20a%20reenactment%20group%20looking%20for%20a%20young%20Henry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20debuted%20my%20impersonation%20with%20the%20group%20on%20a%20voluntary%20basis.%20During%20the%20week%2C%20I'd%20be%20in%20the%20factory%2C%20and%20then%20on%20the%20weekend%2C%20I'd%20self-finance%20my%20trips%20around%20the%20country%20to%20different%20palaces.%20The%20other%20reenactors%20and%20I%20would%20travel%20to%20heritage%20sites%20like%20Penshurst%20Place%20(a%20site%20once%20used%20as%20Henry%20VIII's%20hunting%20lodge)%2C%20where%20we%20would%20perform%20and%20walk%20around%20the%20grounds%20in%20character%2C%20educating%20people%20on%20the%20Tudors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20a%20year%2C%20the%20high%20travel%20costs%20and%20exhaustion%20got%20to%20me%2C%20but%20I%20didn't%20want%20to%20give%20up%20on%20being%20Henry.%20I%20decided%20to%20start%20doing%20it%20as%20paid%20work%3A%20I%20set%20up%20a%20business%20email%20address%20and%20a%20Facebook%20page%20and%20started%20getting%20in%20touch%20with%20palaces%20and%20historic%20workshops%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3E'You%20have%20to%20believe%20that%20you%20are%20the%20king'%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20current%20job%20is%20a%20long%20way%20from%20my%20career%20as%20a%20delivery%20driver%2C%20which%20I%20ended%20just%20last%20year.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20now%20work%20five%20days%20a%20week%20visiting%20schools%2C%20palaces%2C%20and%20other%20heritage%20sites.%20I%20adapt%20to%20what%20the%20venue%20wants%3A%20I%20do%20historical%20talks%2C%20live%20reenactments%20of%20historical%20events%2C%20and%20even%20Tudor%20dancing.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20job%20could%20be%20described%20as%20being%20half%20teacher%2C%20half%20method%20actor.%20Nearly%20every%20time%20I%20go%20into%20a%20school%2C%20a%20kid%20asks%20me%2C%20%26quot%3BIf%20you're%20Henry%20VIII%2C%20how%20are%20you%20still%20alive%3F%26quot%3B%20I%20usually%20reply%2C%20%26quot%3BWell%2C%20God%20wills%20it%20to%20be%20so%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20in%20some%20ways%2C%20I%20have%20to%20believe%20it%20myself.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20do%20the%20job%20well%2C%20you%20have%20to%20believe%20that%20you%20are%20the%20most%20important%20person%20%E2%80%94%20that%20you%20are%20the%20king.%20You%20have%20to%20believe%20that%20you%20were%20chosen%20by%20God.%20All%20that%20definitely%20gives%20you%20confidence%20that%20stays%20with%20you.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Henry%20VIII%20and%20anne%20boleyn%20impersonators%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662134bc20b15f0ff4291ad6%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22812%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmith%20with%20an%20Anne%20Boleyn%20impersonator%20at%20Hatfield%20House.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20I%20took%20part%20in%20a%20three-course%20banquet%20at%20the%20Old%20Palace%20in%20Hatfield%20House%2C%20an%20estate%20previously%20owned%20by%20Henry%20VIII%20and%20now%20owned%20by%20the%20Marquess%20of%20Salisbury.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EVisitors%20could%20dine%20with%20me%20and%20Anne%20Boleyn%20for%20around%20%C2%A380%20(%24100)%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Eper%20person.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20whole%20experience%20was%20as%20historically%20accurate%20as%20possible.%20My%20hands%20were%20washed%20for%20me%2C%20my%20food%20was%20cut%20for%20me%2C%20my%20goblet%20was%20refilled%20whenever%20I%20needed%20it%2C%20and%20everyone%20had%20to%20bow%20and%20curtsey%20to%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOut%20of%20all%20the%20events%20I've%20attended%2C%20that%20was%20the%20one%20that%20made%20me%20feel%20most%20like%20Henry%20VIII.%20I%20felt%20how%20he%20must've%20felt%20being%20there%20and%20being%20served.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EBecoming%20Henry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221024%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Tudor%20reenactment%20group%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F662258af20b15f0ff4297212%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22769%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ESmith%20with%20a%20Tudor%20reenactment%20group.%3Cp%3EDavid%20Smith%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3ESome%20people%20wrongly%20see%20Henry%20as%20just%20an%20obese%2C%20tyrannical%20despot%20of%20a%20King.%20While%20that's%20reflective%20of%20the%20last%20years%20of%20his%20life%2C%20when%20he%20ordered%20the%20execution%20of%20thousands%20of%20people%2C%20that%20wasn't%20always%20how%20he%20was.%20He%20was%20also%20a%20scholar%20and%20a%20well-mannered%20leader.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20incredible%20to%20see%20the%20excitement%20you%20see%20on%20kids'%20faces%20when%20you%20go%20into%20schools%2C%20and%20they%20get%20to%20see%20this%20historic%20character%20brought%20to%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20I'm%20not%20a%20traditional%20teacher%2C%20I%20still%20think%20of%20myself%20as%20one.%20I%20get%20all%20the%20good%20bits%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0meeting%20new%20pupils%20and%20sharing%20my%20passion%20for%20history%20%E2%80%94%C2%A0without%20the%20stress%20that%20teachers%20deal%20with.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAfter%20my%20visit%2C%20one%20school%20sent%20me%20letters%20to%20my%20home%20address%3A%2030%20letters%20from%20children%20expressing%20how%20much%20they%20loved%20my%20visit%20and%20shared%20all%20the%20facts%20they%20remembered.%20That%20was%20a%20particularly%20touching%20moment.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3ELife%20outside%20Henry%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%3Cp%3EUnlike%20my%20old%20job%2C%20I%20have%20to%20take%20my%20role%20home%20with%20me.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMy%20beard%20is%20cut%20in%20the%20same%20way%20Henry%20had%20his%20and%20although%20I'm%20naturally%20blond%2C%20I%20dye%20my%20hair%20and%20beard%20ginger%20to%20improve%20the%20resemblance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIt's%20definitely%20taxing%20on%20my%20time.%20Every%20two%20weeks%2C%20I%20travel%20around%2070%20miles%20to%20practice%20traditional%20Tudor%20dancing%20with%20a%20group.%20And%20even%20when%20I%20come%20home%20from%20a%20long%20day%20at%20work%2C%20all%20I%20want%20to%20do%20is%20get%20straight%20back%20to%20learning%20more%20about%20the%20Tudors.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EA%20lot%20of%20my%20earnings%20go%20back%20into%20the%20business.%20Each%20of%20my%20outfits%20is%20custom-made%20by%20historical%20costumiers%20to%20my%20exact%20measurements.%20Prices%20start%20at%20%C2%A32%2C000%20(%242%2C500)%20%E2%80%94%20and%20that's%20without%20all%20the%20extras%20that%20go%20with%20it%3A%20the%20rings%2C%20the%20chain%20of%20office%2C%20the%20medallions.%20I%20currently%20own%20two%20of%20these%20outfits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EGetting%20the%20money%20together%20takes%20me%20a%20while%2C%20but%20I%20pride%20myself%20on%20accuracy.%20I%20live%20and%20breathe%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EMost%20of%20my%20small%20circle%20of%20friends%20work%20in%20reenactment%20too%2C%20and%20they%20understand%20that%20this%20lifestyle%20is%20a%20defining%20part%20of%20who%20I%20am.%20My%20name%20is%20saved%20as%20Henry%20in%20most%20of%20their%20phones.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWhile%20my%20career%20may%20seem%20a%20long%20way%20off%20from%20other%20people's%20jobs%2C%20I%20still%20have%20the%20same%20concerns%20and%20ambitions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETrying%20to%20%26quot%3Bmake%20it%26quot%3B%20in%20any%20industry%20requires%20a%20level%20of%20sacrifice%2C%20be%20that%20on%20your%20time%20or%20your%20relationships.%20Perhaps%20the%20hardest%20thing%20is%20the%20fear%20of%20running%20out%20of%20bookings%2C%20like%20with%20any%20freelance%20job.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBut%20all%20that%20matters%20to%20me%20is%20that%20I%20have%20enough%20to%20live%20on%20and%20keep%20investing%20in%20this%20passion.%20I%20don't%20really%20care%20for%20buying%20a%20fancy%20house%20or%20fancy%20cars%2C%20I%20just%20want%20to%20earn%20enough%20to%20buy%20Tudor%20books%20and%20add%20to%20my%20collection%20of%20Tudor%20portraits.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI%20could%20never%20go%20back%20to%20a%20'normal'%20job%2C%20I'll%20keep%20doing%20this%2C%20even%20if%20one%20day%20it%20means%20having%20to%20take%20a%20pay%20cut.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-driver-quit-job-to-become-henry-viii-impersonator-unusual-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713694142000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66213e9b10c6b0cde5f0afe0%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-driver-quit-job-to-become-henry-viii-impersonator-unusual-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Henry%20VIII%20impersonator%20David%20Smith%20says%20he%20could%20never%20go%20back%20to%20working%20a%20'normal'%20job%20after%20quitting%20to%20pursue%20his%20passion%20for%20Tudor%20history.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22abacon%40insider.com%20(Alexandra%20Bacon)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A3%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fdelivery-driver-quit-job-to-become-henry-viii-impersonator-unusual-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22IPL%20Live%3A%20Injury%20Scare%20For%20Narine%2C%20KKR%20Worried%20Despite%20Good%20Start%20vs%20RCB%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EKKR%20vs%20RCB%20LIVE%20Cricket%20Score%2C%20IPL%202024%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3A%20Phil%20Salt%20and%20Sunil%20Narine%20have%20given%20a%20brilliant%20start%20to%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20against%20Royal%20Challengers%20Bengaluru%20in%20their%20IPL%202024%20match.%20T