ing%20more%20expensive%2C%20and%20their%20entertainment%20requirements%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ehad%20outgrown%20Chuck%20E.%20Cheese.%20This%20presents%20a%20particular%20challenge%20when%20we%20are%20also%20trying%20to%20tighten%20the%20budget%20to%20deal%20with%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fprices-inflation-rate-rise-drop-deflation-food-oil-car-prices-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Erising%20prices%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ETo%20fit%20the%20needs%20and%20wants%20of%20two%20teenagers%20into%20our%20family%20budget%2C%20we%20first%20came%20up%20with%20a%20new%20plan%20for%20their%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fexpert-advice-kid-allowance-2023-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowance%3C%2Fa%3E%20in%202022%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ethat%20encouraged%20good%20habits.%20The%20next%20step%20was%20to%20get%20them%20involved%20in%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbest-coupon-app-grocery-shopping-deals-discounts-rebates-2023-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efamily%20finances%3C%2Fa%3E%20to%20teach%20them%20about%20budgeting%20and%20the%20importance%20of%20being%20smart%20about%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESince%20we%20adjusted%20the%20family%20finances%2C%20we%20have%20seen%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Epatience%20grow%20in%20terms%20of%20saving%20money%20and%20waiting%20to%20see%20if%20a%20purchase%20is%20truly%20necessary.%20We%20have%20also%20seen%20them%20become%20more%20interested%20in%20budgeting%20and%20smarter%20with%20money.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EHere%20are%20several%20ways%20that%20we%20budget%20around%20two%20teenagers%20and%20teach%20them%20about%20money%20at%20the%20same%20time.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EAllowance%20is%20given%20weekly%20and%20not%20tied%20to%20chores%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22A%20teenager%20doing%20chores.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6620010e49058e669356f5b5%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221667%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EChores%20are%20encouraged%2C%20not%20required.%20The%20author's%20family%20is%20not%20pictured.%20%3Cp%3EImgorthand%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWhen%20my%20spouse%20and%20I%20came%20up%20with%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Ffinancial-plan%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Efinancial%20plan%3C%2Fa%3E%20for%20our%20daughters%20as%20they%20got%20older%20and%20a%20bit%20more%20independent%2C%20we%20first%20understood%20that%20they%20would%20need%20regular%20spending%20money.%20However%2C%20we%20did%20not%20want%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fpersonal-finance%2Funconventional-approach-kids-allowance-2022-4%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eallowance%20to%20be%20performance-based%3C%2Fa%3E.%20That%20is%2C%20we%20decided%20not%20to%20require%20the%20completion%20of%20chores%20or%20other%20tasks%2C%20like%20homework%2C%20for%20them%20to%20receive%20their%20allowance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EEvery%20week%2C%20they%20each%20receive%20%2425%2C%20which%20we%20think%20of%20as%20a%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Faustin-guarunteed-basic-income-gbi-ubi-housing-security-homeless-2024-1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eguaranteed%20basic%20income%20program%3C%2Fa%3E.%20It%20also%20creates%20a%20fixed%20monthly%20expense%20in%20our%20family%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20allowance%20is%20a%20guaranteed%20amount%20they%20can%20count%20on%20each%20month%2C%20and%20the%20money%20does%20not%20come%20with%20any%20strings%20attached.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20an%20old%20saying%20that%20once%20you%20pay%20somebody%20to%20do%20something%2C%20they%20will%20never%20do%20it%20for%20free%20again.%20Our%20goal%20is%20to%20have%20our%20daughters%20be%20responsible%2C%20not%20paid%20workers.%20We%20also%20try%20our%20best%20to%20reward%20good%20behavio