ng%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222500%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Children%20budgeting%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6620083449058e669356f990%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221669%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWe%20encourage%20our%20children%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20family%20finances.%20The%20author's%20family%20is%20not%20pictured.%20%3Cp%3ENickyLloyd%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EWe%20have%20another%20bonus%20system%20for%20the%20girls%20based%20on%20how%20well%20the%20family%20sticks%20to%20the%20monthly%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20our%20family%2C%20the%20budget%20is%20not%20a%20secret.%20We%20encourage%20our%20children%20to%20be%20involved%20in%20the%20family%20finances%20to%20expose%20them%20to%20budgeting%20early%20on.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20the%20end%20of%20each%20month%2C%20we%20all%20review%20how%20the%20month%20went%2C%20where%20we%20did%20well%2C%20and%20what%20we%20could%20have%20done%20better.%20And%20if%20we%20came%20in%20under%20our%20budget%2C%20we%20give%20the%20girls%20a%20profit-sharing%20bonus.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThere%20is%20no%20set%20amount%20or%20rate%20for%20the%20budget%20bonus.%20We%20discuss%20it%20as%20a%20family%20and%20assign%20the%20bonuses%20to%20each%20daughter.%20We%20will%20also%20designate%20a%20third%20%26quot%3Bbonus%26quot%3B%20to%20our%20vacation%20fund%2C%20which%20might%20ultimately%20mean%20an%20extra%20day%20at%20Disney%20or%20a%20little%20extra%20spending%20cash%20for%20the%20girls%20in%20New%20York%20City.%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3EWe%20use%20an%20allowance%20app%20to%20encourage%20good%20money%20habits%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%225477%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Greenlight%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F5ee39cf25af6cc07ac0c012b%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%223651%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EGreenlight%20offers%20debit%20cards%20for%20kids.%20The%20author's%20family%20is%20not%20pictured