articularly%20in%20Russia's%20armed%20forces%20that%20date%20back%20to%20Tsarist%20and%20Soviet%20times%20and%20are%20rife%20with%20corruption%20and%20abuse.%20Yet%20Russia's%20enemies%20can't%20complacently%20assume%20that%20Moscow's%20military%20will%20always%20be%20stuck%20in%20a%20rut%2C%20warns%20a%20US%20expert.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20military%20is%20capable%20of%20reform%2C%20especially%20of%20a%20structural%20nature%2C%26quot%3B%20wrote%20researcher%20Katherine%20Kjellstr%C3%B6m%20Elgin%20in%20a%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fcsbaonline.org%2Fresearch%2Fpublications%2Fmore-of-the-same-the-future-of-the-russian-military-and-its-ability-to-change%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cspan%3Ereport%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cspan%3E%20for%20the%20Center%20for%20Strategic%20and%20Budgetary%20Assessments%20think%20tank%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%20%26quot%3BThat%20does%20not%20mean%2C%20however%2C%20that%20reform%20will%20be%20easy.%20Indeed%2C%20Russia's%20tendency%20to%20seek%20top-down%20structural%20reforms%20matched%20with%20enduring%20characteristics%20of%20the%20Russian%20military%20suggest%20that%20a%20transformation%20of%20the%20Russian%20military%20will%20be%20difficult.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Russian%20military%20is%20unlikely%20to%20substantially%20reform%20in%20the%20short-%20to%20medium-term%2C%26quot%3B%20predicted%20Elgin%2C%20who%20believes%20%26quot%3Bit%20is%20unlikely%20that%20its%20future%20force%20will%20be%20drastically%20different%20in%20character%20from%20the%20Russian%20military%20that%20exists%20today.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Russian%20National%20Guard%20Service%20cadets%20march%20in%20Moscow%20during%20rehearsal%20for%20the%202023%20Victory%20Day%20military%20parade.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622a55883c8ec6e1530224c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221333%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3ERussian%20National%20Guard%20Service%20cadets%20march%20in%20Moscow%20during%20rehearsal%20for%20the%202023%20Victory%20Day%20military%20parade.%3Cp%3EContributor%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EIt's%20not%20that%20Russia%20can't%20adapt%20to%20failure.%20Reforms%20occurred%20after%20the%20Crimean%20War%20of%201853-1856%2C%20yet%20the%20Soviet%20military%20was%20able%20to%20adapt%20quickly%20enough%20to%20transform%20the%20disaster%20of%201941%20%E2%80%94%20when%20Nazi%20German%20troops%20reached%20the%20outskirts%20of%20Moscow%20%E2%80%94%20into%20the%20triumph%20of%201945.%20Today%2C%20Russia%20has%20displayed%20skill%20in%20waging%20drone%20and%20electronic%20warfare%20in%20Ukraine.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EBut%20these%20are%20small%20innovations%20compared%20to%20the%20agile%2C%20NATO-style%20army%20that%20some%20Western%20experts%20claimed%20Russia%20had%20created%20before%20the%20Ukraine%20war%20Putin%20ordered%20in%202022.%20%26quot%3BInstead%2C%20the%20early%20stages%20of%20the%20Russian%20invasion%20exposed%20low%20morale%2C%20brittle%20logistics%2C%20overly%20centralized%20command%20and%20control%2C%20deficiencies%20in%20equipment%2C%20rampant%20corruption%2C%20and%20an%20overreliance%20on%20esoteric%20doctrine%2C%20revealing%20that%20the%20reform%20efforts%20that%20began%20in%202008%20had%20failed%20to%20fully%20deliver%20on%20many%20of%20their%20core%20objectives%2C%26quot%3B%20Elgin%20pointed%20out.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHistorically%2C%20when%20the%20Russian%20military%20does%20change%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20be%20top-down%20reforms%20such%20as%20reorganizing%20military%20districts%20or%20modernizing%20equipment%2C%20rather%20than%20low-level%20tactics%2C%20Elgin%20wrote.%20Even%20when%20leaders%20order%20reforms%2C%20change%20is%20blocked%20by%20%26quot%3Bmilitary%20culture%20that%20does%20not%20encourage%20authority%2C%20a%20lack%20of%20talented%20and%20empowered%20middle%20management%2C%20inaccurate%20information%2C%20and%20a%20lack%20of%20flexibility%20to%20adjust%20course.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThe%20system%20also%20encourages%20pleasing%20superiors%20and%20%26quot%3Bconveying%20the%20appearance%20of%20success%20may%20be%20more%20important%20than%20truly%20making%20progress.%26quot%3B%20To%20be%20fair%2C%20such%20complaints%20about%20style%20over%20substance%20are%20not%20unheard%20of%20in%20the%20US%20or%20other%20militaries.%20But%20this%20problem%20is%20especially%20acute%20in%20Russia's%20highest%20echelons%2C%20where%20apparatchiks%20stifle%20the%20feedback%20and%20criticism%20needed%20to%20identify%20what's%20hampering%20its%20systems%20and%20operations%2C%20including%20the%20Ukraine%20war.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EThis%20doesn't%20rule%20out%20the%20unlikely%20possibility%20that%20Russia%20can%20change%20the%20overall%20culture%20of%20its%20military.%20However%2C%20according%20to%20Elgin%2C%20this%20can%20only%20happen%20if%20two%20conditions%20are%20met%3A%20high-level%20and%20sustained%20political%20support%20and%20adequate%20resources%20are%20made%20available.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EGiven%20that%20observers%20so%20misjudged%20Russian%20military%20capabilities%20prior%20to%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20how%20can%20the%20West%20accurately%20determine%20whether%20reforms%20are%20occurring%3F%20One%20sign%20is%20whether%20top%20Russian%20leaders%20only%20make%20an%20occasional%20speech%20about%20military%20improvement%2C%20or%20whether%20they%20continually%20address%20the%20issue.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAnother%20is%20the%20grievances%20and%20recommendations%20voiced%20by%20younger%20officers%20fresh%20from%20the%20battlefields%20of%20Ukraine%20and%20which%20officers%20are%20being%20promoted%20or%20ignored.%20And%20despite%20Russia's%20authoritarian%20crackdown%20on%20dissent%2C%20voices%20outside%20the%20military%20are%20a%20good%20indicator.%20%26quot%3BThese%20voices%20could%20emerge%20from%20military%20blogs%2C%20the%20intelligence%20services%2C%20or%20private%20military%20companies%2C%26quot%3B%20Elgin%20wrote.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EHowever%2C%20it%20is%20also%20important%20to%20study%20not%20just%20Russian%20officers%2C%20but%20also%20how%20ordinary%20soldiers%20are%20trained%2C%20Elgin%20told%20Business%20Insider.%20%26quot%3BWhat%20are%20they%20teaching%20in%20military%20schools%3F%20How%20are%20troops%20being%20trained%20on%20a%20daily%20basis%3F%20In%20other%20words%2C%20how%20are%20reforms%20being%20rolled%20out%20not%20just%20at%20the%20top%20levels%2C%20but%20how%20are%20they%20affecting%20the%20experience%20of%20every%20service%20member%3F%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EReform%20doesn't%20necessarily%20translate%20into%20battlefield%20performance.%20Despite%20reforms%20instituted%20after%20the%20Crimean%20War%2C%20the%20Russian%20army%20still%20suffered%20from%20command%20control%20and%20other%20flaws%20in%20the%20Russo-Turkish%20War%20of%201877-1878.%20%26quot%3BIt%20is%20possible%20to%20successfully%20achieve%20the%20goals%20you%20set%20out%20in%20a%20reform%20program%2C%20but%20to%20reform%20in%20ways%20that%20do%20not%20result%20in%20success%20on%20the%20battlefield%2C%26quot%3B%20Elgin%20said.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cspan%3EAny%20reforms%20today%20might%20only%20create%20a%20military%20with%20a%20new%20look%20but%20old%20problems.%20%26quot%3BIt%20may%20have%20new%20equipment%2C%20new%20formations%2C%20and%20potentially%20new%20doctrine%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Elgin.%20%26quot%3Bbut%20its%20enduring%20weaknesses%2C%20vulnerabilities%2C%20and%20tendencies%20are%20likely%20to%20remain%20the%20same.%20And%20this%20is%20something%20that%20NATO%2C%20Ukraine%2C%20and%20others%20can%20prepare%20for%20and%20take%20advantage%20of.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3EMichael%20Peck%20is%20a%20defense%20writer%20whose%20work%20has%20appeared%20in%20Forbes%2C%20Defense%20News%2C%20Foreign%20Policy%20magazine%2C%20and%20other%20publications.%20He%20holds%20an%20MA%20in%20political%20science%20from%20Rutgers%20Univ.%20Follow%20him%20on%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.twitter.com%2F%40mipeck1%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ETwitter%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E%20and%20%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.linkedin.com%2Fin%2Fmipeck%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3ELinkedIn%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fa%3E%3Cem%3E%3Cspan%3E.%3C%2Fspan%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-military-is-allergic-to-the-deep-reforms-it-needs-2024-4%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713693601000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F6622a65a0dfb1341e9fd208c%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-military-is-allergic-to-the-deep-reforms-it-needs-2024-4%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Whatever%20the%20outcome%20of%20the%20Ukraine%20war%2C%20one%20thing%20seems%20certain%3A%20the%20Russian%20military%20is%20in%20need%20of%20drastic%20changes.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Michael%20Peck)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A1%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Frussias-military-is-allergic-to-the-deep-reforms-it-needs-2024-4%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Everyone%20hates%20high%20prices.%20So%20why%20are%20we%20all%20still%20spending%20like%20crazy%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%221365%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Photo%20illustration%20of%20a%20100%20dollar%20bill.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F661fee9449058e6693