%20polls%20in%20The%20Maldives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOver%202.8%20lakh%20people%20are%20voting%C2%A0today%20to%20elect%2093%20members%20of%20the%20Maldivian%20parliament%20-%20known%20as%20Majlis%20--%20for%20a%20five-year%20term.%20This%20election%2C%20it%20must%20be%20pointed%20out%2C%20is%20not%20to%20elect%20the%20President.%20Mohamed%20Muizzu%2C%20whose%20anti-India%20stance%20and%20outreach%20to%20China%20has%20made%20international%20headlines%2C%20will%20continue%20to%20be%20in%20the%20top%20post%2C%20irrespective%20of%20the%20results%20in%20the%20national%20election.%20But%2C%20the%20results%20will%20determine%20if%20he%20gets%20the%20political%20muscle%20to%20push%20forward%20policies.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhy%20Maldives%20Election%20Is%20Important%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Muizzu%20came%20to%20power%20in%20the%20elections%20for%20the%20top%20post%20last%20year.%20But%20his%20party%2C%20the%20People's%20National%20Congress%2C%20is%20part%20of%20an%20alliance%20that%20is%20in%20a%20minority%20in%20the%2093-member%20House.%20The%20Maldivian%20Democratic%20Party%2C%20led%20by%20Muizzu's%20pro-India%20predecessor%20Ibrahim%20Mohamed%20Solih%20dominates%20the%20Majlis%20with%2041%20members.%20The%20lack%20of%20parliamentary%20majority%20has%20blocked%20Muizzu's%20policy%20plans%2C%20with%20members%20of%20the%20Opposition%20flagging%20his%20anti-India%20position.%20A%20senior%20aide%20of%20Muizzu%20has%20told%20news%20agency%20AFP%20that%20%26quot%3Bgeopolitics%20is%20very%20much%20in%20the%20background%26quot%3B%20in%20this%20election.%20%26quot%3BHe%20came%20to%20power%20on%20a%20promise%20to%20send%20back%20Indian%20troops%20and%20he%20is%20working%20on%20it.%20The%20parliament%20has%20not%20been%20cooperating%20with%20him.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia%2C%20China%20Watch%20Result%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShortly%20after%20coming%20to%20power%2C%20Muizzu%20pressed%20for%20the%20exit%20of%20a%20small%20