mproved%20sound%20but%20new%20lip-syncing%20allegations%2C%20inciting%20a%20performance%20standards%20debate.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20Entertainment%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22UK%20Sex%20Offender%20Banned%20From%20Using%20AI%20Tools%20Amid%20Deepfakes%20Threat%3A%20Report%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EA%20UK%20court%20has%20banned%20a%20sex%20offender%20from%20using%20any%20%E2%80%9CAI-creating%20tools%E2%80%9D%20for%20the%20next%20five%20years.%20As%20per%20a%20report%20by%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.theguardian.com%2Ftechnology%2F2024%2Fapr%2F21%2Fsex-offender-banned-from-using-ai-tools-in-landmark-uk-case%5C%22%3EThe%20Guardian%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20Anthony%20Dover%20has%20been%20convicted%20of%20making%20more%20than%201%2C000%20indecent%20images%20of%20children.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%2048-year-old%20has%20also%20been%20asked%20to%20pay%20a%20%C2%A3200%20fine.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20report%20added%20that%20this%20ban%20prohibits%20Dover%20from%20using%20text-to-image%20generators%2C%20a%20tool%20that%20can%20create%20lifelike%20pictures%20based%20on%20a%20written%20command.%20In%20addition%2C%20it%20can%20also%20reportedly%20be%20used%20to%20make%20explicit%20%E2%80%9Cdeepfakes%E2%80%9D.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EPointing%20out%20the%20records%20from%20a%20sentencing%20hearing%20at%20Poole%20Magistrates%20Court%2C%20the%20report%20stated%20that%20Dover%20has%20also%20been%20ordered%20to%20stay%20away%20from%20Stable%20Diffusion%20software.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EIt%20must%20be%20noted%20that%20Stable%20Diffusion%20software%20has%20reportedly%20been%20exploited%20by%20paedophiles%20to%20create%20hyper-realistic%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20material.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThis%20case%20was%20reported%20just%20a%20few%20days%20after%20the%20UK%20government%20said%20that%20it%20would%20be%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-to-criminalise-creation-of-sexually-explicit-deepfakes-5453788%5C%22%3Ecriminalising%20the%20creation%20of%20sexually%20explicit%20%26quot%3Bdeep%20fakes%26quot%3B%3C%2Fa%3E%20that%20are%20manipulated%20using%20AI.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EThe%20government%20stated%20that%20people%2C%20who%20create%20deepfakes%20without%20consent%20even%20if%20they%20don't%20intend%20to%20share%20the%20images%20or%20videos%2C%20will%20also%20face%20prosecution.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EBut%20if%20the%20deepfakes%20are%20shared%20widely%2C%20then%20the%20creators%20could%20be%20jailed.%20This%20new%20offence%20will%20be%20introduced%20through%20an%20amendment%20to%20the%20Criminal%20Justice%20Bill.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3ELaura%20Farris%2C%20Minister%20for%20Victims%20and%20Safeguarding%2C%20said%20that%20it%20would%20send%20a%20%26quot%3Bcrystal%20clear%20message%20that%20creating%20deepfakes%20is%20immoral%2C%20often%20misogynistic%2C%20and%20a%20crime%26quot%3B.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%3EShe%20added%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20purpose%20of%20deepfakes%20is%20often%20to%20cause%20alarm%2C%20humiliation%2C%20or%20distress%20to%20the%20victims%20and%20thus%20should%20be%20severely%20dealt%20with.%20It%20is%20another%20example%20of%20ways%20in%20which%20certain%20people%20seek%20to%20degrade%20and%20dehumanise%20others%20-%20especially%20women.%20It%20has%20the%20capacity%20to%20cause%20catastrophic%20consequences%20if%20the%20material%20is%20shared%20more%20widely.%20This%20government%20will%20not%20tolerate%20it.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713690060000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.ndtvimg.com%2Fi%2F2016-04%2Fessex-uk-police-generic_650x400_41459521365.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fuk-court-bans-sex-offende