eary%20eyes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESubani%20said%20that%20he%20and%20his%20wife%20have%20been%20living%20separately%20for%20the%20past%20six%20years%20and%20that%20Fayaz%20stayed%20with%20his%20mother%20and%20called%20him%20whenever%20he%20needed%20money.%20He%20last%20spoke%20to%20his%20son%20about%20three%20months%20ago.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EFayaz's%20father%20recalled%20that%20around%20eight%20months%20ago%2C%20Neha%20Hiremath's%20family%20had%20called%20him%20to%20inform%20that%20his%20son%20was%20troubling%20their%20daughter.%20Admitting%20that%20his%20son%20made%20a%20mistake%2C%20he%20said%20that%20Fayaz%20and%20Neha%20loved%20each%20other%20and%20were%20in%20a%20relationship.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BFayaz%20told%20me%20he%20wanted%20to%20marry%20her%20but%20I%20refused%20it%20by%20folding%20my%20hands%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECondemning%20his%20son's%20act%2C%20Fayaz's%20father%20said%20that%20no%20one%20should%20commit%20any%20such%20atrocities%20against%20women.%C2%A0%26quot%3BI%20request%20the%20people%20of%20Karnataka%20to%20forgive%20me.%20My%20son%20has%20done%20wrong.%20He%20will%20be%20punished%20by%20the%20law%20of%20the%20land%20and%20I%20welcome%20it.%20My%20town%20has%20got%20a%20black%20mark%20because%20of%20my%20son.%20People%20of%20Munavalli%20(Fayaz's%20hometown)%20please%20forgive%20me.%20You%20raised%20us.%20Please%20forgive%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20cried%20with%20folded%20hands.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20the%20victim's%20family%20has%20been%20demanding%20that%20the%20accused%20be%20hanged%20to%20death%20and%20only%20then%20will%20their%20daughter's%20soul%20rest%20in%20peace.%20They%20maintained%20that%20their%20daughter%20was%20not%20in%20a%20relationship%20with%20Fayaz%20and%20said%20the%20accused%20stabbed%20Neha%20because%20she%20rejected%20his%20proposal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThere%20were%20protests%20in%20several%20parts%20of%20the%20state%20demanding%20capital%20punishment%20for%20Fayaz%2C%20who%20has%20been%20arrested%20in%20connection%20with%20the%20incident%20that%20occurred%20on%20April%2018.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20alleged%20murder%20of%20the%20daughter%20of%20the%20city%20corporation%20councillor%20on%20her%20college%20campus%20has%20sparked%20widespread%20condemnation%20and%20protests.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20issue%20has%20snowballed%20into%20a%20political%20slugfest%20between%20the%20ruling%20Congress%20and%20opposition%20BJP%20in%20Karnataka.%20While%20the%20ruling%20party%20has%20tried%20to%20project%20it%20as%20an%20%26quot%3Bincident%20with%20a%20personal%20angle%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20saffron%20party%20suspects%20%26quot%3Blove%20jihad%26quot%3B%20and%20said%20that%20it%20points%20to%20the%20%26quot%3Bdeterioration%20of%20law%20and%20order%26quot%3B%20in%20the%20state.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20was%20allegedly%20stabbed%20to%20death%20on%20the%20campus%20of%20BVB%20College%20on%20Thursday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20accused%20Fayaz%20Khondunaik%2C%20who%20fled%20the%20scene%2C%20was%20arrested%20by%20police%20subsequently.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENeha%20was%20a%20first-year%20MCA%20student%20and%20Fayaz%20was%20her%20former%20classmate.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20senior%20police%20officer%2C%20Fayaz%20allegedly%20stabbed%20her%20multiple%20times.%20During%20interrogation%2C%20he%20claimed%20that%20the%20two%20had%20been%20in%20a%20relationship%20but%20she%20had%20been%20avoiding%20him%20of%20late.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20needs%20to%20be%20corroborated%20and%20verified%2C%20but%20he%20was%20arrested%20immediately%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20officer%20said.%20PTI%20AMP%20SDP%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%3Ci%3E(Except%20for%20the%20headline%2C%20this%20story%20has%20not%20been%20edited%20by%20NDTV%20staff%20and%20is%20published%20from%20a%20syndicated%20feed.)%3C%2Fi%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713687840000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F7p3is14o_karnataka-murder-protest-pti_625x300_20_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22orig