al.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Add%20image%20caption%20here%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F7cqb86co_tihar-jail_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAdd%20image%20caption%20here%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cbr%3E%5CnSoon%20after%20the%20AAP%20Ministers's%20flip-flop%20charge%2C%20the%20jail%20administration%20said%20that%20a%20senior%20doctor%20from%20AIIMS%20was%20consulted%20via%20video%20conferencing%20following%20a%20request%20by%20the%20Chief%20Minister's%20wife%20Sunita%20Kejriwal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAfter%20a%20detailed%20consultation%2C%20Arvind%20Kejriwal%20was%20assured%20that%20there%20was%20no%20serious%20concern%20and%20was%20advised%20to%20continue%20with%20the%20prescribed%20medicines%2C%20which%20will%20be%20evaluated%20and%20reviewed%20on%20a%20regular%20basis%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20administration%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Bharadwaj%20and%20Delhi%20Minister%20Atishi%20had%20yesterday%20claimed%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20is%20being%20pushed%20towards%20%26quot%3Bslow%20death%26quot%3B%20by%20being%20denied%20insulin%20and%20consultations%20with%20his%20doctors.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAtishi%20said%20that%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20used%20to%20take%2050%20units%20of%20insulin%20daily%20before%20he%20was%20sent%20to%20jail.%20%26quot%3BAt%20the%20behest%20of%20the%20BJP%2C%20a%20conspiracy%20is%20underway%20to%20kill%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20in%20jail.%20The%20chief%20minister%20has%20been%20taking%20insulin%20for%2012%20years%2C%20what%20is%20the%20problem%20for%20the%20Tihar%20administration%20to%20give%20insulin%20to%20him%3F%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20asked.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Tihar%20administration%20maintains%20that%20there%20is%20adequate%20availability%20of%20insulin%20in%20the%20jail%20dispensary%20and%20it%20can%20be%20administered%20to%20Mr%20Kejriwal%20%26quot%3Bas%20and%20when%20required.%