th%20them%20for%20a%20better%20future%20they%20deserve.%20These%20people%20are%20my%20strength%20and%2C%20'inshallah'%2C%20I%20will%20win.%20With%20the%20kind%20of%20positive%20mindset%20I%20am%20currently%20in%2C%20I%20am%20not%20even%20thinking%20of%20the%20possibility%20of%20a%20loss%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathan%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20contesting%20from%20the%20prestigious%20Baharampur%20Lok%20Sabha%20seat%20in%20Murshidabad%20district%20of%20West%20Bengal%20on%20a%20Trinamool%20Congress%20ticket%2C%20and%20has%20emerged%20as%20the%20prime%20challenger%20to%20Congress%20veteran%20and%20incumbent%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20on%20his%20home%20turf.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20the%20utmost%20respect%20for%20Adhir%20Chowdhury%2C%20who%20is%20a%20senior%20leader%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBut%20when%20I%20listen%20to%20people%2C%20I%20hear%20discontentment%20over%20his%20absence%20from%20grassroots%20during%20the%20Covid%20years.%20People%20here%20allege%20that%20Chowdhury%20failed%20to%20bring%20in%20the%20required%20central%20grants%20to%20create%20infrastructure%20and%20employment%20opportunities.%20There's%20not%20enough%20work%20for%20people%20and%20the%20MP%20of%2025%20years%20should%20answer%20people%20why%20he%20failed%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20hard-hitting%20former%20cricketer%2C%20who%20moved%20from%20Gujarat%20to%20fight%20for%20a%20seat%20on%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20floor%20from%20Bengal.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathan%20listed%20creating%20job%20opportunities%20to%20hold%20migrant%20workers%20back%2C%20building%20a%20world-class%20sports%20complex%2C%20infrastructure%20for%20local%20silk%2C%20thermocol%20and%20jute%20industry%20workers%2C%20and%20creating%20a%20support%20system%20for%20farmers%20as%20priority%20areas%20of%20work%2C%20should%20Baharampur%20voters%20choose%20him%20as%20their%20representative%20in%20Parliament.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20a%20lot%20of%20work%20to%20do%20here.%20I%20have%20figured%20that%20out%20in%20my%20short%20presence%20in%20the%20region%2C%20during%20my%20poll%20campaigns%20and%20interactions%20with%20people%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJoining%20the%20Lok%20Sabha%20poll%20fray%2C%20however%2C%20was%20possibly%20the%20last%20thing%20on%20Pathan's%20mind%20barely%20a%20month%20and%20a%20half%20ago%20till%20Mamata%20Banerjee%20(CM%20and%20TMC%20supremo)%20and%20her%20nephew%20Abhishek%20approached%20him.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20happened%20less%20than%20a%20week%20ahead%20of%20the%20day%20the%20party%20declared%20its%20candidate%20list%20on%20March%2010%2C%26quot%3B%20Pathan%20said.%20%26quot%3BMy%20first%20response%20was%20negative.%20I%20was%20swinging%20on%20the%20horns%20of%20a%20dilemma%20on%20whether%20or%20not%20to%20accept%20the%20offer.%20After%20all%2C%20I%20had%20never%20given%20a%20serious%20thought%20to%20politics%20before%2C%20nor%20was%20I%20a%20particular%20fan%20of%20the%20craft%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20stated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20what%20eventually%20made%20him%20choose%20politics%20and%20the%20TMC%2C%20Pathan%20said%20with%20a%20hearty%20laugh%3A%20%26quot%3BCricket%20toh%20khatam%20ho%20gaya%2C%20kuch%20toh%20karna%20tha%20(my%20cricketing%20days%20were%20over%20and%20I%20had%20to%20do%20something).%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BOn%20a%20serious%20note%2C%20I%20consulted%20my%20family%2C%20including%20my%20brother%20Irfan%20and%20wife%20Afreen.%20I%20also%20spoke%20to%20my%20seniors%20and%20friends.%20I%20soon%20realised%20that%20this%20could%20actually%20be%20a%20gift%2C%20an%20opportunity%20from%20the%20Almighty%20to%20serve%20the%20people%20and%20give%20back%20to%20society%20what%20I%20earned%20all%20these%20years%20in%20terms%20of%20love%20and%20respect%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathan%2C%20though%2C%20maintained%20he%20was%20familiar%20with%20Mamata%20Banerjee's%20politics%20for%20over%20a%20decade%2C%20particularly%20since%202011%20when%20he%20began%20playing%20for%20the%20Kolkata%20Knight%20Riders%20in%20the%20IPL.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20used%20to%20come%20and%20stay%20in%20Bengal%20for%20months%20and%20could%20see%20the%20civic%20infrastructure%20developments%20she%20brought%20to%20Kolkata.%20People%20kept%20telling%20me%20about%20her%20work%20in%20areas%20of%20women's%20education%20and%20for%20the%20poor.%20I%20even%20met%20her%20in%202014%20after%20KKR%20won%20the%20IPL%20that%20season%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recounted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BHence%2C%20saying%20yes%20to%20her%20offer%20wasn't%20much%20of%20an%20issue%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Pathan.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20if%20his%20religious%20identity%2C%20that%20of%20a%20devout%20Muslim%2C%20gave%20him%20an%20edge%20over%20opponents%20in%20a%20Muslim-majority%20seat%20like%20Baharampur%2C%20Pathan%20firmly%20dissociated%20religion%20from%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20have%20respect%20for%20every%20religion%20in%20this%20county%2C%20but%20people%20should%20not%20be%20treated%20as%20vote%20banks%20based%20on%20their%20religious%20identities.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BElections%20should%20be%20fought%20for%20both%20majority%20and%20minority%20communities%2C%20not%20for%20one%20or%20the%20other.%20The%20priority%20should%20be%20the%20growth%20of%20economy%20and%20development%20of%20people%20so%20that%20we%20can%20build%20a%20future%20for%20our%20next%20generation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20asserted.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathan%2C%20who%20was%20also%20an%20effective%20off%20spinner%2C%20continues%20to%20maintain%20a%20deep%20attachment%20to%20cricket%20despite%20bidding%20adieu%20to%20the%20game's%20professional%20formats.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPathan%20said%20his%20identity%20as%20a%20cricketer%20would%20continue%20to%20dominate%20his%20newfound%20love%20for%20politics.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20my%20identities%20are%20important%2C%20none%20of%20which%20I%20can%20hide.%20But%2C%20people%20will%20always%20consider%20me%20a%20cricketer%20first.%20They%20have%20seen%20me%20play%20and%20loved%20me%20for%20my%20performances%20in%20the%20middle.%20Now%2C%20they%20can%20expect%20me%20to%20serve%20them%20as%20one%20of%20their%20own%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20someone%20who%20sweated%20it%20out%20on%20the%20field%20under%20rigorous%20training%20schedules%2C%20Pathan%20feels%20the%20heat%20and%20dust%20of%20Baharampur%20have%20only%20added%20a%20leaf%20to%20his%20experience%20in%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTo%20the%20dust%2C%20we%20shall%20all%20return.%20'Dhool%20se%20kya%20darna'%20(why%20fear%20it)%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713684780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-03%2Fnp0mt0m_yusuf-pathan-ani_625x300_12_March_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhere-to-stay-in-politics-cricketer-politician-yusuf-pathan-5489357%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Former%20Indian%20cricketer-turned-politician%20Yusuf%20Pathan%2C%20the%20TMC's%20face%20against%20Congress%20heavyweight%20Adhir%20Ranjan%20Chowdhury%20in%20Baharampur%2C%20says%20he%20is%20here%20to%20stay%20in%20politics.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A2%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhere-to-stay-in-politics-cricketer-politician-yusuf-pathan-5489357%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhere-to-stay-in-politics-cricketer-politician-yusuf-pathan-5489357%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fhere-to-stay-in-politics-cricketer-politician-yusuf-pathan-5489357%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Spain%E2%80%99s%20%E2%80%98Society%20of%20the%20Snow%2C%E2%80%99%20%E2%80%9820%2C000%20Species%20of%20Bees%E2%80%99%20Sweep%20the%20Platino%20Awards%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713684780000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fvariety.com%2Fwp-content%2Fuploads%2F20