g%20implemented%20in%20the%20marquee%20T20%20tournament%20for%20almost%20two%20editions%20now%2C%20there%20have%20been%20a%20lot%20of%20expert%20opinions%20about%20it%2C%20with%20majority%20of%20them%20going%20against%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BNow%20that%20such%20an%20observation%20has%20been%20made%2C%20we%20will%20definitely%20look%20into%20it.%20We%20will%20discuss%20with%20all%20parties%20involved%20and%20then%20take%20a%20call%2C%26quot%3B%20Dhumal%20told%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.telegraphindia.com%2Fsports%2Fcricket%2Frohit-sharma-poser-on-impact-player-puts-board-of-control-for-cricket-in-india-on-backfoot%2Fcid%2F2014487%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EThe%20Telegraph%3C%2Fa%3E%20on%20Friday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThere%20are%20various%20pros%20and%20cons%20to%20any%20rule%20that%20is%20in%20place.%20We%20are%20open%20to%20any%20discussion%20once%20the%20season%20gets%20over...%20nothing%20is%20cast%20in%20stone%20about%20its%20implementation%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEarlier%2C%20Rohit%2C%20who%20plays%20for%20Mumbai%20Indians%20in%20IPL%2C%20had%20explained%20how%20the%20impact%20player%20rule%20is%20taking%20the%20all-rounders'%20role%20out%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20not%20a%20big%20fan%20of%20Impact%20sub%20rule.%20It%20is%20going%20to%20hold%20all%20rounders%20back%2C%20eventually%20cricket%20is%20played%20by%2011%20players%20not%2012%20players.%20You%20are%20taking%20out%20so%20much%20from%20game%20to%20make%20it%20entertaining%20for%20people%20around.%20If%20you%20look%20just%20from%20the%20cricketing%20aspect%20of%20it%20I%20feel%20guys%20like%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Shivam%20Dube%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F107521-shivam-dubey-playerprofile%5C%22%3EShivam%20Dube%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20%3Ca%20title%3D%5C%22Washington%20Sundar%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Fcricket%2Fplayers%2F108593-washington-sundar-