ating%20the%20matter.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20has%20been%20reported%20in%20Musrigharari%2C%20a%20small%20town%20in%20Samastipur%20district%2C%20about%2080%20km%20from%20state%20capital%20Patna.%20Relatives%20of%20Babita%20Devi%20have%20said%20that%20they%20brought%20her%20to%20Anisha%20healthcare%20centre%20for%20a%20sterilisation%20surgery.%20The%20small%20healthcare%20centre%20is%20on%20the%20first%20floor%20of%20a%20two-storey%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20relatives%20of%20the%20woman%20have%20said%20that%20the%20staff%20at%20the%20centre%20had%20told%20them%20that%20no%20doctor%20was%20available.%20Then%2C%20the%20compounder%20proceeded%20to%20conduct%20the%20surgery.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20brought%20her%20here%20around%209%20am.%20They%20administered%20her%20saline%20water.%20Around%2011%20am%2C%20they%20started%20the%20procedure.%20About%20an%20hour%20later%2C%20they%20put%20her%20into%20an%20ambulance%20and%20rushed%20her%20to%20a%20hospital%20in%20Mohanpur%20(about%2010%20km%20away)%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20woman's%20uncle%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20added%20that%20the%20family%20members%20were%20not%20told%20anything%20about%20her%20condition%2C%20but%20when%20they%20touched%20her%20to%20check%2C%20the%20body%20was%20cold.%20%26quot%3BShe%20died%20right%20here.%20But%20they%20did%20not%20tell%20us%20and%20rushed%20to%20Mohanpur%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOnce%20Babita%20Devi's%20death%20was%20confirmed%2C%20her%20relatives%20brought%20the%20body%20back%20to%20Anisha%20health%20care%20centre%20and%20held%20a%20protest.%20Heart-rending%20visuals%20showed%20an%20elderly%20relative%20calling%20out%20to%20the%20dead%20woman.%20The%20family%20alleged%20that%20no%20health%20care%20centre%20in%20Musrigharari%20town%20has%20a%20doctor%20and%20junior%20staff%20--%20known%20as%20compounders%20--%20were%20performing%20all%20medical%20procedures%20and%20risking%20patients'%20lives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20staff%20of