nd-seven-missing-after-two-japanese-navy-helicopters-crash-into-the-ocean-13119966%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Microsoft's%20New%20AI%20App%20Makes%20Mona%20Lisa%20Sing%2C%20Internet%20Calls%20It%20''Crazy''%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EMicrosoft%20recently%20introduced%20a%20new%20artificial%20intelligence%20(AI)%20model%20that%20can%20generate%20hyper-realistic%20videos%20of%20talking%20human%20faces.%20Dubbed%20VASA-1%2C%20the%20AI%20image-to-video%20model%20can%20transform%20still%20photos%20of%20people's%20faces%20into%20lively%20animations.%20The%20company%20says%20the%20created%20videos%20will%20have%20synchronised%20lip%20movements%20to%20match%20the%20audio%20as%20well%20as%20facial%20expressions%20and%20head%20movement%20to%20make%20it%20appear%20natural.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ERecently%2C%20a%20video%20demonstrating%20the%20app's%20capabilities%20went%20viral%20on%20social%20media%2C%20leaving%20people%20amazed.%20The%20AI-generated%20video%20shows%20Mona%20Lisa%2C%20the%20iconic%20painting%20by%20Leonardo%20da%20Vinci%2C%20lip-syncing%20to%20Anne%20Hathaway's%3Cem%3E%20'Paparazzi'.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''Microsoft%20just%20dropped%20VASA-1.%20This%20AI%20can%20make%20a%20single%20image%20sing%20and%20talk%20from%20audio%20reference%20expressively.%20Similar%20to%20EMO%20from%20Alibaba.%2010%20wild%20examples%3A%201.%20Mona%20Lisa%20rapping%20Paparazzi%2C''%20the%20caption%20of%20the%20thread%20shared%20by%20Min%20Choi%20reads.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EWatch%20the%20video%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%20just%20dropped%20VASA-1.%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnThis%20AI%20can%20make%20single%20image%20sing%20and%20talk%20from%20audio%20reference%20expressively.%20Similar%20to%20EMO%20from%20Alibaba%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn10%20wild%20examples%3A%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5Cn1.%20Mona%20Lisa%20rapping%20Paparazzi%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FLSGF3mMVnD%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FLSGF3mMVnD%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20Min%20Choi%20(%40minchoi)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2Fminchoi%2Fstatus%2F1780792793079632130%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2018%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20video%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20with%20some%20being%20amused%20by%20the%20funny%20clip.%20One%20user%20wrote%2C%20''The%20Mona%20Lisa%20clip%20had%20me%20rolling%20on%20the%20floor%20laughing.''%20Another%20commented%2C%20''Oh%2C%20man.%20If%20only%20Da%20Vinci%20could%20witness%20this.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESome%20also%20expressed%20their%20concerns%20about%20its%20unethical%20usage%2C%20especially%20to%20create%20deep%20fakes.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20wrote%2C%20''Creepy%3F%20Fascinating%3F%20For%20one%20thing%2C%20deepfake%20potential%20just%20grew%20exponentially%E2%80%A6but%20opens%20up%20some%20interesting%20creative%20possibilities%20as%20well.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''Deepfake%20Tech%20Just%20Took%20a%20Terrifying%20Leap%20Forward%20and%20it's%20more%20convincingly%20deceptive%20than%20we%20ever%20imagined.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.microsoft.com%2Fen-us%2Fresearch%2Fproject%2Fvasa-1%2F%5C%22%3EMicrosoft%2C%3C%2Fa%3E%C2%A0VASA%20is%20a%20framework%20for%20generating%20lifelike%20talking%20faces%20of%20virtual%20characters%20with%20appealing%20visual%20affective%20skills%20(VAS).%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''VASA-1%2C%20is%20capable%20of%20not%20only%20producing%20lip%20movements%20that%20are%20exquisitely%20synchronized%20with%20the%20audio%2C%20but%20also%20capturing%20a%20large%20spectrum%20of%20facial%20nuances%20and%20natural%20head%20motions%20that%20contribute%20to%20the%20perception%20of%20authenticity%20and%20liveliness.%C2%A0The%20core%20innovations%20include%20a%20holistic%20facial%20dynamics%20and%20head%20movement%20generation%20model%20that%20works%20in%20a%20face%20latent%20space%2C%20and%20the%20development%20of%20such%20an%20expressive%20and%20disentangled%20face%20latent%20space%20using%20videos%2C''%20the%20company%20wrote.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''We%20have%20no%20plans%20to%20release%20an%20online%20demo%2C%20API%2C%20product%2C%20additional%20implementation%20details%2C%20or%20any%20related%20offerings%20until%20we%20are%20certain%20that%20the%20technology%20will%20be%20used%20responsibly%20and%20by%20proper%20regulations%2C''%20Microsoft%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713683160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fdsk77aro_mona-lisa-singing_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fviral-video-microsofts-new-ai-app-makes-mona-lisa-sing-internet-calls-it-crazy-5489119%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22The%20AI-generated%20video%20shows%20Mona%20Lisa%2C%20the%20iconic%20painting%20by%20Leonardo%20da%20Vinci%2C%20lip-syncing%20to%20Anne%20Hathaway's%20'Paparazzi'.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fviral-video-microsofts-new-ai-app-makes-mona-lisa-sing-internet-calls-it-crazy-5489119%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fviral-video-microsofts-new-ai-app-makes-mona-lisa-sing-internet-calls-it-crazy-5489119%2Famp%2F1%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Foffbeat%2Fviral-video-microsofts-new-ai-app-makes-mona-lisa-sing-internet-calls-it-crazy-5489119%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Teenager%20killed%20by%20crocodile%20as%20boat%20breaks%20down%20in%20Australia%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713682848000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-109472895%2Cimgsize-75170.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fteenager-killed-by-cr