he%20wants%20to%20run%20London%20like%20a%20%26quot%3Bseasoned%20CEO%26quot%3B%20who%20delivers%20profits%20for%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDelhi-born%20Tarun%20Ghulati%20believes%20his%20experience%20as%20a%20businessman%20and%20investment%20expert%20is%20what%20London%20needs%20to%20revive%20its%20fortunes%20as%20the%20%26quot%3Bglobal%20bank%20of%20the%20world%26quot%3B%20by%20attracting%20the%20investment%20it%20needs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2063-year-old%20is%20standing%20as%20an%20Independent%20candidate%20among%2013%20contestants%20in%20the%20fray%20for%20the%20local%20elections%20on%20May%202%20when%20Londoners%20will%20vote%20for%20their%20Mayor%20and%20also%20for%20members%20of%20the%20London%20Assembly.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20view%20London%20as%20a%20unique%20global%20city%2C%20akin%20to%20the%20'global%20bank%20of%20the%20world'%20where%20diverse%20cultures%20converge%20to%20flourish%2C%26quot%3B%20Ghulati%20said%20in%20a%20speech%20this%20week.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAs%20Mayor%2C%20I%20will%20build%20London's%20balance%20sheet%20such%20that%20it%20is%20the%20premier%20choice%20for%20investment%2C%20safeguarding%20safety%20and%20prosperity%20for%20all%20its%20residents.%20I%20will%20transform%20and%20run%20London%20effectively%20and%20efficiently%20like%20a%20seasoned%20CEO.%20London%20will%20be%20a%20profitable%20corporation%20where%20profitability%20means%20the%20well-being%20of%20all.%20You%20will%20all%20be%20part%20of%20the%20journey.%20Let's%20do%20it%20for%20our%20London%2C%20our%20home%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESafety%20on%20the%20streets%20of%20the%20city%20is%20among%20his%20other%20major%20priorities%2C%20with%20visible%20community%20policing%20and%20more%20officers%20patrolling%20on%20the%20beat%20on%20the%20agenda.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIt%20is%20about%20having%20enough%20bobbies%20on%20the%20beat%2C%20having%20the%20resources%20for%20police%20officers%20to%20do%20their%20jobs%3B%20which%20means%20making%20the%20streets%20safe%20for%20women%20to%20walk%20at%20night%2C%20with%20muggers%20and%20burglars%20being%20caught%20and%20punished%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EScrapping%20some%20of%20the%20Labour%20Party%20incumbent%20Sadiq%20Khan's%20unpopular%20policies%20such%20as%20the%20high%20costs%20associated%20with%20Ultra%20Low%20Emissions%20Zone%20(ULEZ)%20charges%20and%20Low%20Traffic%20Neighbourhoods%20(LTNs)%20across%20the%20city%20also%20make%20up%20Ghulati's%20key%20policy%20planks.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BWe%20did%20not%20want%20ULEZ%2C%20LTNs%20or%2020mph%20speed%20limits%20and%20many%20other%20poor%20policies...%20Climate%20change%20is%20happening%20and%20we%20need%20to%20mitigate%20its%20effects%20but%20that%20cannot%20be%20done%20by%20making%20everyone%20live%2015%20minutes%20from%20home%20or%20to%20penalise%20commuters%20in%20areas%20with%20little%20public%20transport.%20What%20changes%20we%20need%20to%20make%20must%20be%20paced%20with%20public%20opinion%2C%20not%20imposed%20arbitrarily%20on%20wallets%20coping%20with%20the%20cost%20of%20living%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ghulati%2C%20who%20has%20called%20London%20his%20home%20for%2020%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20is%20equally%20scathing%20about%20the%20Conservative%20Party%20candidate%20for%20Mayor%2C%20Susan%20Hall%2C%20who%20he%20claims%20failed%20to%20block%20the%20Mayor's%20controversial%20policies%20despite%20being%20an%20assembly%20member%20for%20London%20for%20many%20years.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20would%20not%20be%20a%20candidate%20for%20Mayor%20if%20the%20political%20candidates%20were%20doing%20what%20they%20should%20be.%20They%20have%20let%20us%20down.%20This%20is%20all%20about%20London%20and%20Londoners%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20declared.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECreating%20more%20affordable%20housing%2C%20minimising%20council%20tax%2C%20increasing%20focus%20on%20tourism%20to%20the%20UK%20capital%20and%20ensuring%20free%20school%20meals%20are%20among%20some%20of%20Ghu