ed-ceo-5488577%2Famp%2F1%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Uber%20Bans%20Woman%20Called%20Swastika%20Chandra%20Over%20Her%20Name%2C%20Later%20Apologises%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20woman%20was%20banned%20from%20using%20Uber's%20ride-share%20and%20food%20delivery%20service%20because%20her%20first%20name%20was%20flagged%20as%20offensive.%20According%20to%20the%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fnypost.com%2F2024%2F04%2F20%2Flifestyle%2Fswastika-chandra-banned-from-uber-app-for-unusual-first-name%2F%5C%22%3ENew%20York%20Post%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%2C%C2%A0Australian%20woman%2C%20Swastika%20Chandra%20explained%20her%20first%20name%20meant%20''good%20luck''%20in%20Sanskrit%20and%20it%20was%20a%20common%20name%20in%20Fiji%2C%C2%A0where%20she%20grew%20up.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20happened%20in%20October%20last%20year%20when%C2%A0Ms%20Chandra%20attempted%20to%20order%20food%20from%20Uber%20Eats.%20During%20the%20payment%20stage%2C%20she%20received%20a%20notification%C2%A0informing%20her%20that%20her%20name%20violated%20the%20company's%20terms.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''I%20was%20putting%20in%20an%20order%20for%20food%20one%20afternoon%20and%20went%20to%20the%20payment%20stage%20and%20this%20pop-up%20came%20up%20saying%2C%20'Your%20first%20name%20is%20in%20violation%20and%20you%20need%20to%20change%20your%20name%20on%20the%20app%2C''%20the%2035-year-old%20told%20%3Cem%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2F9now.nine.com.au%2Fa-current-affair%2Fuber-bans-sydney-woman-from-using-service-because-of-her-first-name%2F2771dd1f-b9fd-4ba6-8045-671145bc0c02%5C%22%3EA%20Current%20Affair.%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENotably%2C%C2%A0in%20Western%20contexts%2C%20the%20term%20is%20predominantly%20linked%20with%20the%20Nazi%20Party%20of%20Germany.%C2%A0It%20took%20five%20months%20and%20the%20intervention%20of%20the%20Hindu%20Council%20of%20Australia%20and%20the%20New%20South%20Wales%20attorney-general%20to%20get%20her%20account%20reinstated.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''They%20don't%20know%20that%20the%20Hindus%20used%20it%20for%20thousands%20of%20years%20before%20Hitler%20used%20it%20in%20the%20wrong%20way.%20It%20is%20a%20very%20common%20name.%20I%20know%20four%20or%20five%20other%20girls%20with%20the%20same%20name.%20In%20school%2C%20we%20had%20two%20or%20three%20other%20girls%20with%20the%20same%20name%20%E2%80%93%20It%20means%20good%20luck%20and%20it%20means%20good%20things%20for%20me.%20I'm%20very%20proud%20of%20my%20name.%20I%20believe%20in%20the%20good%20that%20comes%20with%20it%20and%20I'm%20not%20changing%20it%20for%20anyone%2C''%20she%20added.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Jewish%20Board%20of%20Deputies%20also%20backed%20Ms%20Chandra's%20fight%2C%20telling%20%3Cem%3EA%20Current%20Affair%3A%3C%2Fem%3E%20%26quot%3BThere%20is%20a%20difference%20between%20Ms%20Chandra%20innocently%20using%20her%20name%20and%20the%20deployment%20of%20a%20sinister%20symbol.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EUber%20also%20issued%20an%20apology%20to%20Ms%20Chandra%20and%20issued%20a%20statement.%20''Uber%20is%20committed%20to%20facilitating%20a%20safe%20and%20welcoming%20environment%20for%20all%20users.%C2%A0For%20that%20reason%2C%20Uber%20has%20a%20global%20policy%20of%20restricting%20access%20to%20users%20whose%20names%20entered%20into%20the%20Uber%20app%20contain%20potentially%20offensive%20words.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWe%20understand%20that%20there%20are%20different%20cultural%20nuances%20to%20names%2C%20and%20therefore%20our%20teams%20address%20incidents%20like%20this%20on%20a%20case-by-case%20basis%20to%20ensure%20we%20evaluate%20each%20account%20fairly.%20In%20this%20case%2C%20after%20reviewing%20MS.%20Chandra's%20request%2C%20we%20reinstated%20her%20access%20to%20the%20app.%20We%20have%20apologized%20to%20Ms%20Chandra%20for%20the%20inconvenience%20this%20caused%20her%2C%20and%20we%20appreciate%20her%20patience%20as%20we%20reviewed%20the%20matter%2C%20which%20took%20longer%20than%20we%20hoped%20it%20would%2C''%20the%20statement%20read.%