pay%20would%20barely%20cover%20my%20family%20expenses.%20Around%20this%20time%2C%20I%20came%20to%20know%20about%20donkey%20rearing%20in%20south%20India.%20I%20met%20some%20people%20and%20set%20up%20this%20farm%20in%20my%20village%20about%208%20months%20back%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20started%20with%2020%20donkeys%20and%20an%20investment%20of%20Rs%2022%20lakh.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20beginning%20was%20tough.%20There%20is%20hardly%20any%20demand%20for%20donkey%20milk%20in%20Gujarat%2C%20and%20Mr%20Solanki%20earned%20nothing%20in%20the%20first%20five%20months.%20He%20then%20started%20reaching%20out%20to%20companies%20in%20south%20India%2C%20where%20there%20is%20a%20demand%20for%20donkey%20milk.%20He%20now%20supplies%20to%20Karnataka%20and%20Kerala%2C%20and%20among%20his%20clients%20are%20cosmetic%20companies%20that%20use%20donkey%20milk%20in%20their%20products.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2F41vq3pr_gujarat-man_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAsked%20about%20the%20rate%2C%20Mr%20Solanki%20says%20it%20ranges%20between%20Rs%205%2C000%20to%20Rs%207%2C000%20--%20compare%20this%20to%20cow%20milk%20sold%20at%20Rs%2065%20a%20litre.%20The%20milk%20is%20stored%20in%20freezers%20to%20ensure%20it%20stays%20fresh.%20The%20milk%20is%20dried%20and%20sold%20in%20powdered%20form%20too%2C%20with%20prices%20going%20up%20to%20about%20a%20lakh%20for%20kg.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMr%20Solanki%20now%20has%2042%20donkeys%20in%20his%20farm%20and%20has%20invested%20about%2038%20lakh%20rupees%20so%20far.%20He%20says%20he%20has%20not%20taken%20any%20help%20from%20the%20state%20government%20so%20far%2C%20but%20wants%20it%20to%20focus%20on%20this%20sector%20too.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Benefits%20Of%20Donkey%20Milk%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDonkey%20milk%20was%20widely%20used%20in%20the%20ancient%20times%2C%20with%20some%20accounts%20claiming%20that%20Egyptian%20queen%20Cleopatra%20used%20to%20bathe%20in%20it.%20Greek%20physician%20Hippocrates%2C%20the%20father%20of%20medicine%2C%20is%20learnt%20to%20have%20prescribed%20donkey%20milk%20for%20liver%20problems%2C%20nosebleeds%2C%20poisonings%2C%20infectious%20diseases%20and%20fevers.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDespite%20its%20many%20benefits%2C%20the%20prevalence%20of%20donkey%20milk%20saw%20a%20decline%20in%20the%20modern%20era%2C%20before%20scientists%20rediscovered%20its%20potential.%20Availability%2C%20though%2C%20is%20still%20limited%20and%20this%20explains%20the%20high%20prices.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAccording%20to%20a%20report%20in%20US'%20National%20Library%20of%20Medicine%2C%20donkey%20milk's%20composition%20is%20more%20similar%20to%20human%20milk%20compared%20to%20cow%20milk%20and%20makes%20it%20a%20great%20choice%20for%20infants%2C%20especially%20those%20who%20are%20allergic%20to%20cow%20milk.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BAnother%20important%20aspect%20of%20donkey%20milk%20in%20the%20medical%20field%20is%20its%20ability%20to%20regulate%20intestinal%20microflora%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20report%20says%2C%20detailing%20its%20benefits%20in%20ensuring%20better%20gut%20health.%20There%20are%20also%20studies%20that%20point%20to%20its%20benefits%20in%20boosting%20immunity%20and%20anti-diabetic%20qualities.%20Donkey%20milk%20is%20also%20known%20to%20have%20a%20higher%20shelf%20life%20as%20it%20doesn't%20contain%20several%20pathogens%20found%20in%20other%20forms%20of%20milk.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713677700000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fvvi163vg_donkey-farm_625x300_21_April_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Findia-news%2Fdonkey-milk-gujarat-man-sets-up-donkey-farm-sells-milk-online-at-rs-5-000-a-litre-5488943%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22For%20centuries%2C%20they%20have%20been%20