ms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-50-dead-after-a-boat-capsizes-in-central-african-republic%2Farticleshow%2F109470334.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F109470334.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EOver%2050%20died%20as%20a%20boat%20capsized%20en%20route%20to%20a%20funeral%20in%20Bangui%2C%20Central%20African%20Republic.%20Eyewitnesses%20reported%20an%20overcapacitated%20boat%20with%20a%20wooden%20structure.%20Local%20rescuers%2C%20including%20boat%20pilots%20and%20fishermen%2C%20aided%20in%20the%20search%20and%20rescue%20operations.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22TOI%20World%20Desk%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-50-dead-after-a-boat-capsizes-in-central-african-republic%2Farticleshow%2F109470334.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-50-dead-after-a-boat-capsizes-in-central-african-republic%2Famp_articleshow%2F109470334.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Frest-of-world%2Fat-least-50-dead-after-a-boat-capsizes-in-central-african-republic%2Famp_articleshow%2F109470334.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22CA's%20Viral%20Post%20On%20Salary%20Comparison%20With%20IAS%20Officer%20Sparks%20Debate%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EBecoming%20an%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20officer%20is%20one%20of%20the%20most%20prestigious%20and%20sought-after%20careers%20in%20India.%20However%2C%20a%20chartered%20accountant%20(CA)%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20X%20when%20he%20said%20he%20didn't%20understand%20why%20people%20chose%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20despite%20the%20low%20salary.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ECA%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20compared%20the%20salary%20of%20an%20IAS%20officer%20with%20his%20profession%2C%20noting%20that%20the%20average%20salary%20of%20an%20IAS%20is%20the%20starting%20salary%20of%20a%20CA.%C2%A0He%20also%20shared%20a%20photo%20showing%20an%20IAS%20officer's%20salary%20division.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E''The%20average%20salary%20of%20an%20IAS%20is%20the%20starting%20salary%20of%20a%20CA%20Why%20do%20people%20prefer%20IAS%3F''%20he%20wrote.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESee%20the%20post%20here%3A%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20class%3D%5C%22twitter-tweet%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cp%20dir%3D%5C%22ltr%5C%22%20lang%3D%5C%22en%5C%22%3EThe%20average%20salary%20of%20an%20IAS%20is%20the%20starting%20salary%20of%20a%20CA%3Cbr%3E%5Cn%3Cbr%3E%5CnWhy%20do%20people%20prefer%20IAS%3F%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ft.co%2FKpODLY8F9i%5C%22%3Epic.twitter.com%2FKpODLY8F9i%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%E2%80%94%20CA%20Chirag%20Chauhan%20(%40CAChirag)%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftwitter.com%2FCAChirag%2Fstatus%2F1780616410798182771%3Fref_src%3Dtwsrc%255Etfw%5C%22%3EApril%2017%2C%202024%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fblockquote%3E%5Cn%5Cn%3Cp%3EHis%20tweet%20has%20gone%20viral%2C%20garnering%20an%20array%20of%20reactions.%20Some%20users%20said%20that%20people%20prefer%20IAS%20not%20because%20of%20the%20money%2C%20but%20the%20''respect%20and%20power''%20the%20position%20brings.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20user%20wrote%2C%20''Have%20you%20ever%20heard%20of%20an%20IAS%20ever%20reporting%20to%20a%20CA%3F%20Ever!%3F%20(Unless%20the%20CA%20is%20a%20senior%20govt%20employee%20or%20a%20minister).''%C2%A0Another%20commented%2C%20''Power%20and%20respect.%20Rewards%20are%20bigger%20than%20money.%20Also%2C%20a%20lot%20of%20your%20expenses%20are%20taken%20care%20of%20for%20life.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20third%20wrote%2C%20''There%20is%20no%20comparison%20with%20any%20profession.%20Total%20seats%20of%20IAS%20in%20India%20are%20less%20than%20total%20no%20of%20CA's%20qualify%20every%20attempt.%20Every%20year%20only%20180%20IAS%20are%20selected%20in%20India.%20IAS%20cadre%20seats%20are%20based%20on%20the%20population%20and%20size%20of%20the%20state.%20CA%20is%20one%20of%20the%20best%20post-qualification%20course%20for%20higher%20studies.%20People%20make%20their%20career%20in%20the%20area%20in%20which%20they%20wish%20to%20make%20according%20to%20their%20strength%20%26amp%3B%20ability.%20There%20are%20almost%202%20crore%20students%20who%20clear%20class%2012th%20every%20year%20and%20they%20choose%20their%20career%20in%20any%20field.%20No%20relation%20to%20salary%2C%20it%20depends%20upon%20the%20passion%2C%20knowledge%20%26amp%3B%20focus%20on%20anything%20we%20wish%20to%20do.''%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%20fourth%20added%2C%20''People%20wanting%20to%20join%20IAS%20are%20not%20motivated%20by%20money%20they%20are%20motivated%20by%20desire%20to%20serve%20people.''%20A%20fifth%20wrote%2C%20''When%20you%20started%20as%20CA%20did%20you%20start%20your%20career%20in%20manegerial%20position%2C%20did%20your%20office%20lend%20you%20a%20car%20and%20free%20petrol%2C%20driver%2C%20servant%2C%20house(TBH%20bungalow)%20in%20prominent%20area!%3F%3F''%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1713671160000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-04%2Fqkbs34og_ca-chirag-chauhan_625x300_21_April_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchartered-accountants-post-on-salary-comparison-with-ias-officer-sparks-debate-5488355%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22A%20chartered%20accountant%20(CA)%20sparked%20a%20debate%20on%20X%20when%20he%20said%20he%20didn't%20understand%20why%20people%20chose%20the%20Indian%20Administrative%20Service%20(IAS)%20despite%20the%20low%20salary.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Ffeature%2Fchartered-accountants-post-on-salary-comparison-with-ias-officer-sparks-debate-5488355%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww-ndtv-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2