s%2F2024%2F04%2FCopy-of-Cover-image-25-1713281348-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347427%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3ESandhya%20is%20pursuing%20her%20masters%20from%20the%20University%20for%20Peace%20in%20Costa%20Rica%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEven%20as%20her%20mother%20managed%20to%20secure%20admission%20to%20a%20reputed%20private%20school%2C%20the%20school%20years%20were%20traumatic%20for%20Sandhya.%20%E2%80%9CIt%20started%20with%20bullying%20over%20my%20skin%20colour.%20They%20would%20call%20me%20different%20names%2C%20including%20a%20%E2%80%98black%20crow%E2%80%99%20and%20more.%20After%20a%20few%20years%2C%20they%20found%20out%20that%20my%20mother%20is%20a%20sex%20worker%2C%20and%20the%20bullying%20intensified%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20shares.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIt%20was%20not%20just%20students%2C%20she%20recalls%2C%20but%20even%20teachers%20would%20ridicule%20her%20and%20turn%20a%20blind%20eye%20to%20the%20horrendous%20acts%20committed%20by%20the%20other%20students%20towards%20her.%20Recalling%20a%20particularly%20horrific%20incident%20of%20abuse%2C%20Sandhya%20states%20that%20her%20classmates%20once%20pushed%20her%20head%20into%20a%20commode%20and%20told%20her%2C%20%E2%80%9CYou%20belong%20here%2C%20stay%20here.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EShe%20adds%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20was%20always%20made%20to%20sit%20on%20a%20separate%20bench%20at%20the%20back%20and%20was%20often%20pushed%20around%20in%20corridors%20and%20thrown%20into%20bathrooms.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EBeing%20mistreated%20in%20school%20affected%20young%20Sandhya%E2%80%99s%20academic%20performance%20as%20well.%20Moreover%2C%20it%20didn%E2%80%99t%20help%20that%20sadly%20she%20was%20also%20experiencing%20abuse%20at%20home.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CI%20was%20raped%20multiple%20times%20when%20I%20was%20between%2010%20and%2016%20years%20old.%20My%20abuser%20would%20warn%20me%20that%20if%20I%20told%20anyone%20about%20it%2C%20no%20one%20would%20believe%20me.%20Every%20time%20he%20abused%20me%2C%20he%20told%20me%20that%20I%20deserved%20this.%20I%20heard%20the%20same%20thing%20everywhere%20that%20I%20deserved%20all%20the%20abuse%20because%20of%20my%20background%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20adds.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EEssentially%2C%20she%20says%20she%20was%20being%20conditioned%20to%20hate%20her%20mother%20and%20her%20background.%20She%20confesses%20to%20hating%20herself%20and%20her%20mother%20for%20a%20very%20long%20time.%20As%20Sandhya%20grew%20up%2C%20her%20father%20fell%20sick%2C%20necessitating%20her%20to%20work%20part-time.%20She%20worked%20at%20a%20fast-food%20restaurant%20and%20was%20given%20the%20job%20of%20cleaning%20garbage.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20abuse%20continued%20even%20here%20when%20the%20manager%20found%20out%20about%20her%20background%20and%20tried%20to%20touch%20her%20inappropriately.%20%E2%80%9CThey%20think%20they%20own%20you%2C%E2%80%9D%20remarks%20Sandhya.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti3-1713281068.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22For%20many%20girls%2C%20Kranti%20provides%20a%20new%20lease%20on%20life%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti3-1713281068.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti3-1713281068-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti3-1713281068-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti3-1713281068-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2Fkranti3-1713281068-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347425%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20