%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CIt%20broke%20my%20heart%20to%20see%20girls%20with%20so%20much%20potential%20wasting%20their%20lives%20due%20to%20lack%20of%20access%20to%20resources%20and%20opportunities.%20They%20were%20usually%20just%20married%20off.%20With%20another%20person%20I%20met%20at%20the%20NGO%2C%20Bani%2C%20we%20started%20Kranti%20in%202011%2C%20to%20enable%20these%20girls%20to%20achieve%20their%20full%20potential%2C%E2%80%9D%20Robin%20tells%20%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Better%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20word%20%E2%80%98%3Cem%3Ekranti%3C%2Fem%3E%E2%80%99%20means%20revolution%20and%20the%20girls%20at%20the%20NGO%20are%20called%20%3Cem%3EKrantikaris%3C%2Fem%3E%20meaning%20revolutionaries.%20Robin%20realised%20that%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F315650%2Fforced-into-sex-work-karnataka-sex-worker-helps-hundreds-get-rights-fight-violence%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Egirls%20from%20Kamathipura%3C%2Fa%3E%20and%20other%20red-light%20areas%20have%20immense%20potential%20to%20be%20agents%20of%20change%2C%20not%20%E2%80%98despite%E2%80%99%20their%20background%2C%20but%20rather%20because%20of%20it.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CWe%20believe%20that%20by%20providing%20access%20to%20the%20same%20training%2C%20opportunities%2C%20and%20resources%20as%20people%20from%20privileged%20backgrounds%2C%20they%20will%20become%20revolutionary%20leaders%20%E2%80%94%20more%20innovative%2C%20compassionate%2C%20and%20resilient%20due%20to%20their%20life%20experiences.%20We%20want%20to%20harness%20their%20power%20as%20agents%20of%20social%20change%2C%E2%80%9D%20adds%20Robin.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20provides%20shelter%2C%20education%2C%20support%20and%20opportunities%20for%20girls%20between%20the%20ages%20of%2012%20and%2021.%20Kranti%20has%20its%20own%20school%20with%20six%20teachers%20and%20a%20curriculum%20that%20includes%20English%2C%20reading%2C%20writing%2C%20geography%2C%20music%2C%20creative%20thinking%2C%20yoga%2C%20and%20meditation%2C%20along%20with%20regular%20school%20subjects%2C%20health%2C%20and%20more.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EKranti%20also%20has%20a%20social%20justice%20curriculum%20which%20covers%2020%20topics%20such%20as%20caste%2C%20class%2C%20religion%2C%20environment%2C%20gender%2Fsexuality%2C%20and%20women%E2%80%99s%20rights.%20The%20girls%20are%20taught%20about%20the%20problems%20and%20what%20they%20can%20do%20to%20solve%20them.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20NGO%20equips%20students%20to%20join%20mainstream%20schools%2C%20if%20they%20wish%20to%2C%20or%20help%20others%20through%20open%20schooling.%20While%20many%20girls%20have%20gone%20abroad%20to%20study%2C%20for%20some%2C%20just%20managing%20to%20stay%20afloat%20is%20a%20big%20win%2C%20according%20to%20Robin%2C%20which%20is%20why%20therapy%20is%20given%20so%20much%20importance%20here.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%20810px)%20100vw%2C%20810px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%22810%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Kranti%20runs%20it's%20own%20school%20for%20the%20girls%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710.jpg%20810w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710-300x169.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710-500x281.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710-768x431.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FC0045T01-1713280710-150x84.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-347419%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22455%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EKranti%20runs%20its%20own%20school%20for%20the%20girls%3C%2Ffigc