u%2C%20and%20heard%20that%20there%20was%20a%20gym%20there%20that%20wanted%20to%20recruit%20fighters.%20He%20was%20told%20that%20the%20gym%20there%20would%20take%20care%20of%20all%20his%20living%20expenses.%20So%2C%20he%20came%20back%20to%20Bengaluru%20once%20again%20and%20began%20training.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20second%20stint%20in%20Bengaluru%20would%20change%20Chungreng%E2%80%99s%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CHere%2C%20I%20met%20Coach%20Ashwin%20Hoon%20of%20Warrior%E2%80%99s%20Cove%20MMA%2C%20a%20gym%20based%20out%20of%20Gurugram%2C%20who%20was%20there%20for%20a%20seminar.%20I%20loved%20the%20way%20he%20was%20teaching%20us%20and%20the%20techniques%20he%20was%20showing%20us%2C%20but%20more%20than%20that%2C%20he%20was%20just%20a%20very%20good%20person.%20I%20knew%20that%20if%20I%20trained%20under%20him%2C%20I%20would%20improve.%20He%20was%20the%20coach%20I%20was%20looking%20for%20all%20this%20time.%20I%20didn%E2%80%99t%20care%20about%20dropping%20the%20sponsorship%20I%20was%20getting%20in%20Bengaluru.%20So%2C%20I%20spoke%20to%20Ashwin%20Sir%20and%20made%20my%20way%20to%20Delhi-NCR%20to%20train%20at%20Warrior%E2%80%99s%20Cove%20MMA%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20recalls.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-captioned%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4c5xolpyjQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26amp%3Butm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC4c5xolpyjQ%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26utm_campaign%3Dloading%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3EView%20this%20post%20on%20Instagram%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3Cdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%20%3Cdiv%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%3C%2