%20says%2C%20%E2%80%9CThe%20rows%20in%20which%20saplings%20are%20to%20be%20planted%20must%20be%20in%20the%20direction%20from%20east%20to%20west%2C%20per%20the%20wind%20in%20the%20region%2C%20so%20that%20saplings%20do%20not%20get%20uprooted%20in%20storms.%20Also%2C%20saplings%20are%20planted%20at%20least%20one%20foot%20deep%20into%20the%20ground.%20We%20keep%20the%20distance%20of%2010%C3%9710%20feet%20between%20saplings%20and%20rows.%20Also%2C%20lemons%20thrive%20in%20soil%20that%20has%20a%20pH%20between%206%20and%207%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20informs.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnand%20says%20he%20adopted%20the%20low-cost%20and%20high-profitability%20approach%20to%20growing%20lemons%20and%20placed%2050%20plants%20of%20%3Cem%3Emosambi%3C%2Fem%3E%20(sweet%20lime)%20among%20400%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thebetterindia.com%2F205409%2Forganic-farming-rajasthan-earning-lakhs-lemons-pickle-india%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Elemon%20trees%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHe%20adds%20that%20he%20uses%20both%20organic%20and%20inorganic%20ways%20to%20fertilise%20the%20soil%20and%20control%20pest%20attacks.%20%E2%80%9CBefore%20monsoon%2C%20I%20add%2015%20kg%20of%20compost%20to%20every%20tree%20to%20get%20a%20good%20yield.%20Along%20with%20this%2C%20I%20add%20fertilisers%20like%20DAP%2C%20urea%2C%20and%20potash.%20Although%20no%20chemicals%20are%20used%20in%20natural%20farming%2C%20we%20were%20forced%20to%20use%20chemicals%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F04%2FLemon-farming-3-1712930272.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22More%20than%20the%20huge%20profits%2C%20Anand%20finds%20contentment%20in%20leading%20a%20stress-free%20life%20in%20the%20village.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebett